    <item>
      <title>美国组建团队应对中国“胁迫”策略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/us-firm-steps-in-when-china-is-seen-as-a-bully-not-a-partner</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当韩国决定部署美国反弹道导弹系统时，来自邻国中国的利润丰厚的游客突然枯竭。当澳大利亚指责北京干涉其国内政治并要求解答Covid-19的起源时，中国停止购买煤炭、葡萄酒和牛肉等出口产品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/us-firm-steps-in-when-china-is-seen-as-a-bully-not-a-partner</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
